strings: <voice_0x0100174D><se_low>King of tricks: There is still a long way to go.
<voice_0x0100174E><se_low>King of tricks: A lot happened along the way. But it works.
<voice_0x0100174F><se_low>King of tricks: The old commitments no longer make sense. The most important thing is to live a happy and fulfilling life.
<voice_0x01001750><se_low>King of tricks: You decide for yourself who you want to get married to. Take your time and only take what you need with you.
<voice_0x01001751><se_low>King of tricks: I can't believe how easy it is to find someone new after Prince's divorce...
<voice_0x01001752><se_high>Media princess: Dad, it looks like you forgot! We are at home! Come back home any time!
